{
  "id": "RAW_0203a2",
  "title": "云栖现场｜让评测与标注成为 AI 进化引擎！阿里发布全新评测平台，3 大创新评测集亮相",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk3NTc1NTU0Mw==&mid=2247501147&idx=2&sn=619a6e546a7b0c50c065d4ec997b4303",
  "date": "2025-09-26 13:01:00",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;mfqovyqj5i7cwiik45w&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;bold&quot;:true,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;“当我们不再需要评测时，AGI或许才真正到来 ......”&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;mftmtop79l6xff0dt1v&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(15, 17, 21)&quot;,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;但在抵达那个终极目标之前，一套能够精准衡量其演进轨迹的“标尺”，正变得前所未有的重要。&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"vBPlN5jkrbV83OdG\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“当大模型不再关注刷榜时，AGI或许才真正到来 ......”</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1nbr\">9月26日，位于杭州云栖小镇的“2025云栖大会评测标注分论坛”上，阿里巴巴AI数据总经理魏虎（空望），正式发布了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">阿里巴巴新一代的大模型评测平台“晓天衡宇”SKYLENAGE</span>，以及分别针对数学竞赛、数学推理与游戏代码生成三大高难度领域的创新评测集：SKYLENAGE-Math、SKYLENAGE-ReasoningMath和SKYLENAGE-GameCodeGym。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0id2ui1bgo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279963\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(150, 150, 150) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 3px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f228403d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wucNvbUYZh1e3eMCWic4fvFY47shRsLYickXYWOVaYaib1aicGI0HYHnlcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvimrx120j\">这场主题为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“繁星共绘：构建开放的AI评测标注新生态”</span>的论坛，汇聚了来自北京大学、北京电影学院、Innodata、Turing等顶尖院校与机构的专家学者，以及海内外数十家大模型数据服务商，共同围绕大模型评测与数据标注的前沿发展、国际实践与行业挑战展开深度对话，聚焦AI评测与数据标注的技术突破与生态共建，加速推进模型评测与标注的标准化、专业化和国际化进程，为人工智能的高质量发展提供了交流的舞台。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 16px;\">\n    <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n     <div style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 661px;border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(150, 218, 252);line-height: 2em;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: -5px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(34, 125, 255);min-width: 1em;text-align: left;color: rgb(34, 125, 255);line-height: 1.5;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1zbt\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyx9gzbl1e\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyx9gzg1490\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">晓天衡宇：以评测驱动AI进化</span></span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1ra8\">传统基准评测已难以匹配AGI发展的速度与复杂性，正面临数据污染、评估维度单一、滞后于技术迭代等多重挑战。魏虎（空望）在论坛演讲中指出，亟需构建一个系统、客观、权威的评测体系，打造以“评测驱动”为核心的高质量数据飞轮机制，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">让评测不仅是衡量AI能力的尺子，更要成为推动AI持续进化的重要引擎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0ibsg519li\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279965\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5503412969283277\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2344\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wkPnoJo9lXicQIAlkIjrA3T6GNphw1rlyaF2SMy61KKf8nEld22XOQJg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"545\" data-cropsely2=\"363\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3b812c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wkPnoJo9lXicQIAlkIjrA3T6GNphw1rlyaF2SMy61KKf8nEld22XOQJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvimrx1vr0\">高质量、高难度、高专业度的标注与动态评测体系，是实现模型持续进化的重要前提。通过高考真题、IMO竞赛题等实战案例，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">阿里巴巴的AI数据团队</span>展示了其敏捷、深度的评测能力，“晓天衡宇”SKYLENAGE应运而生。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyvq0gwzeh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279964\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6555209953343701\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2572\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wpQl1IibZR2g06oHxVia6icTuD9zcSRgL9d67Zatz5l1lkMPicDosRjJSnw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"545\" data-cropsely2=\"371\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=57fb4cd5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wpQl1IibZR2g06oHxVia6icTuD9zcSRgL9d67Zatz5l1lkMPicDosRjJSnw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1mph\">“晓”与“衡”，象征着评测的清晰洞察和聚焦分析，代表着智慧、经验和公正的判断；“天”与“宇”，则表明了这一评测平台的广阔视野和宏大格局。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这既是一把衡量AI模型的“高度”与“深度”的“量天之尺”，也是客观评测模型优劣的“高悬明镜”。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1bor\">作为一个全领域评测体系，SKYLENAGE广泛覆盖语言理解与安全、多模态生成、AI4Science、行业任务、智能体决策与具身交互以及产品体验等维度，旨在通过开放可复现的基准与真实环境模拟，为模型的研发、选型与应用提供可靠参考，推动AGI健康、可信发展。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 661px;border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(150, 218, 252);line-height: 2em;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-bottom: -5px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(34, 125, 255);min-width: 1em;text-align: left;color: rgb(34, 125, 255);line-height: 1.5;\">\n        <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyvsi6q1zbt\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfyx9gzbl1e\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyx9gzg1490\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">繁星共绘：从技术挑战到生态共建</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfyyefx94dj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">来自北京大学王选计算机研究所的万小军教授，在云栖大会的舞台上指出，评测是引导大模型技术发展的“灯塔”，但当前正面临着数据失效、敏感、污染与评测困难等诸多问题。评测技术也正朝着自动化构建与动态更新、污染检测、训练专用评测/奖励模型、效用驱动以及人机协同等方向快速发展。</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">构建可靠、高效、可解释的评测体系，是实现大模型健康发展和可信应用的关键所在。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0i2bor19rh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279952\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19913e66&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wtSNHo3jxGrnambcjT6DZyWvPHAYicgxeOvBDibnpVn6u9gRDeEZUFmaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfyyefx94dj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">北京电影学院摄影系副系主任齐虹教授，从资深导演与教育者的双重视角出发，以优酷AIGC作品《大唐狄公案》《闪耀吧！大运河》为例，阐述多模态视频生成亟需融入专业艺术评价维度，呼吁</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">建立覆盖叙事、光影、运镜等维度的权威评测基准，以推动AIGC在影视领域的深度应用，共同迎接智能影视新时代的到来。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0i12c023id\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279953\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7a9292c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9wFLknYwZ3ibc7hb3ibQ9ib2xsr9oibj2xbUEvdTiaiaGyqALt7SMMhOjR04icQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfyyefx94dj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Innodata首席语言数据科学家Jonathan Steuck博士，在大会上分享了从全球视角出发的评测机遇与挑战。Jonathan认为，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI评估体系正经历三大关键演变：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">从评估单一文本生成转向复杂智能体与多用例协同；从依赖人工通用评估发展为“领域专家+大模型”协同的AI增强评估；从以美国为中心的标准转向多元文化对齐。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0i202lfqg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279954\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34edb3fc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0H3REshgy4licJuK9mDjjam626JicjKW9w3vwLyTfv8CviawJSJKkq0YXNtCAgibLmsLCesVzRn4GztPB9vicXFKUicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfyyefx94dj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">如何定义全面的大模型评测维度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，是需要全球共同面对的技术难题，Turing技术副总裁Kai Du分享了其团队为前沿AI实验室构建专业领域评估基准的最新实践。通过高度自动化的数据生成与严格质量审查流程，Turing在三个月内高效构建了超过2000个高质量数据点，涵盖Verilog RTL设计、CUDA内核开发等多个硬科技领域，覆盖从代码生成到系统集成的多样任务，彰显专业评估对技术闭环的关键价值。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0i474k12cn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502279955\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c83979a&amp;u=https%3A%